{"tid":1338323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事實證明邊個再話唔好搞中聯辦邊個就係鬼！","createTime":"2019-07-21T13:00:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T14:30:31.000Z","uid":104764,"like":94,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9fc96b186b958192fa2c21b5201d9310a62dcc61","tid":1338323,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:00:33.000Z","msg":"你搞立法會  政總  林鄭都don&rsquo;t give a shit<br />\n你今日圍中聯辦   幾粒鐘唔夠即清場<br />\n其實今日遊行完  大家都會有疑問：跟住去邊？<br />\n大會亦都冇明確旨示  <br />\n但今日一事   已經睇得好清楚<br />\n林鄭  成個港共政權   視中聯辦比屋企  立法會 特首辦 政總 更重要<br />\n如果要再遊行   終點一定係中聯辦<br />\n唔好再講d咩驚激嬲共產黨呢d咁無知既說話<br />\n五年前嘅失敗我哋唔想再重蹈覆轍<br />\n你打得呢場仗   敵人一開始就係共產黨   港共只係卒仔係傀儡<br />\n如果你話驚得罪佢   咁所有抗爭活動可以立即壽終正寢   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對準政權  不撒不散！"},{"pid":"28ad154f60ef3894f9a765e73b772b1db1fad1bc","tid":1338323,"uid":258217,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"同意，但同時里次成功係因為連義士們一開始都唔知去邊，所以驚察先咁驚，下次去中聯辦，一定要有戰略，再唔係落返中環，立會，或其他政府機關"},{"pid":"110b6a6cc07b084d19c520168f087f2e719aa5c0","tid":1338323,"uid":260594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:04:32.000Z","msg":"攻其不備"},{"pid":"ce920791f157da3d71897177ae372ed9bbba633c","tid":1338323,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:06:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f681f88f748a7772d07d10c54467f4c39987d8da","tid":1338323,"uid":57424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:06:34.000Z","msg":"一向都覺得呢個位置先係終點，一路條直路"},{"pid":"0fa814daa2cfe65500359e4239233a0bad23e4a9","tid":1338323,"uid":80763,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:07:05.000Z","msg":"警署被圍 &gt; 冇反應<br />\n中聯辦被圍 &gt; 立即清場<br />\n你班散仔見唔見到D高層緊張緊D咩人<br />\n話就話同袍 其實就當你地係踏腳石 用完即棄"},{"pid":"20fca3e8a78124316780ce8e5bfe999e3079a661","tid":1338323,"uid":66202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:07:58.000Z","msg":"今次升旗禮同中聯辦都搞齊晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b8468a334378094b18af888425aeb2b7532d3d","tid":1338323,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"元朗手足 返屋企食飯前記得換衫同轉車<br />\n<br />\n有老豆拎住藤條守狗鐵出口想教仔<br />\n<br />\n夾份坐的士 唱K 訓晚酒店 放尋下心情都好架<br />\n<br />\n疊羅漢好危險 玩唔過<br />\n<br />\n求AIR DROP"},{"pid":"543425678e5fc9505dadb9bb429822a5fc3b2fea","tid":1338323,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cfdd2133128066f5f69b1f66f7ab726de94a51bd","tid":1338323,"uid":165997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfdf143560f7249aec0a57346db1ef893969be36","tid":1338323,"uid":47524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"SET做每次必到景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e348233cf322716c97f02cd257c04731991fcfab","tid":1338323,"uid":104764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfdf143560f7249aec0a57346db1ef893969be36","tid":1338323,"uid":47524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:20:53.000Z","msg":"SET做每次必到景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:18:29.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"ba8da9d0b6112d1ad3a5d39a9fd288b636a440ee","tid":1338323,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:24:11.000Z","msg":"做對了"},{"pid":"264e5fc87f96c905efebc65581d19872ee78bcda","tid":1338323,"uid":2